The default quotas on a new GCP subscription are not sufficient for a typical production
level <%= vars.ops_manager_first %> deployment. This topic lists the quotas that you need for a
typical <%= vars.ops_manager %> deployment.

For a single <%= vars.ops_manager %> deployment, ensure that you have the following quotas.

